title: TOO OLD TOO FAT: ONE
description:
This is what happens when you get a bunch of old guys together and out of the office for a day in LA and force them to street skate.

In order of appearance: Ryan Bodman, Rich Dodds, Eric Rovegno, Matt Finelli, Ben Kelly, and Dan Rhoades.

Shot and Edited by: Ransacker
